-reportedly-release-pixel-watch-2-this-fall-213015367.html">Google Pixel Watch 2</a>将于今年秋季推出——有望带来更多新功能。</p>本文最初出现在 Engadget 上，网址为 https://www.engadget.com/googles-pixel-watch-now-offers-overnight-blood-oxygen-tracking-170050532.html?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/googles-pixel-watch-now-offers-overnight-blood-oxygen-tracking-170050532.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> 224b0de4-fe32-477a-937f-77d6d225eee2</guid><dc:creator>莎拉菲尔丁</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>Engadget</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder> Engadget</dc:rightsholder><pubDate> Tue, 13 Jun 2023 17:00:50 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1685963238</ingested><modified> 2023-06-05T11:07:19+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Sarah Fielding]]></category><media:content height="1333" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2022-10/fefe3bb0-49a1-11ed-babb-298ac0d5e8f4" width="2000"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="1333" medium="image" url="https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2022-10/fefe3bb0-49a1-11ed-babb-298ac0d5e8f4" width="2000"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[2]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[Cherlynn Low / Engadget]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[The Pixel Watch on a person's wrist showing the time with three complications below it.]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[Google Pixel Watch]]></media:title></media:content></item><item><title><![CDATA[Pixel phones receive a slew of new features like improved car crash detection]]></title><description type="html"><![CDATA[<p>谷歌刚刚在系统更新中为 Pixel 智能手机用户添加了一系列新功能。首先， <a data-i13n="cpos:1;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/2019-09-30-google-car-crash-detection-pixel-us.html">车祸检测功能有了重大改进，</a>它现在不仅可以联系紧急服务，还可以自动与紧急联系人共享实时位置信息。为此，该更新还允许语音控制，使启动紧急共享或安排安全检查变得更加容易。</p><p>录音功能在这里得到了重大更新，具有将转录本导出到 Google 文档并根据发言者生成标签的新功能，这样您以后就可以轻松找到想要的剪辑。照片定时器也得到了更新，让您可以通过抬起手掌开始倒计时来启动自拍照片。这仅适用于 Pixel 6 手机及更新机型。</p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><p>如果您拥有<a data-i13n="cpos:2;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/google-pixel-7-and-pixel-7-pro-review-still-the-best-bargain-in-flagship-phones-170031940.html">广受好评的 Pixel 7 Pro，</a>则会更新微距对焦功能，因为该功能现在可以处理静态摄影和视频，以获得甲虫爬花或其他任何东西的详细镜头。对于所有 Pixel 手机用户来说，Google Assistant 正在焕发光彩，提供一系列新的语音选项和新的语言选项。如果没有某种表情符号 tomfoolery，它也不会是系统更新，因此有新的表情符号壁纸可以让您混合和匹配具有图案和颜色的图像以创建独特的背景。此更新通过动态电影 (3D) 选项带来了更多壁纸优点。</p><p> Pixel Watch 用户在这里并没有被冷落，因为有一个新的心率工具可以跟踪你的阈值的上限和下限，一个自动暂停工具和期待已久的血氧跟踪器。这些功能现在正在下降，但可能需要几天或几周的时间，更新才会到达您的设备。</p>本文最初出现在 Engadget 上，网址为 https://www.engadget.com/pixel-phones-receive-a-slew-of-new-features-like-improved-car-crash-detection-170045659.html?src=rss ]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/pixel-phones-receive-a-slew-of-new-features-like-improved-car-crash-detection-170045659.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> 4cedc1a1-f9f8-4915-bf17-0e3c75bb458f</guid><dc:creator>劳伦斯邦克</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>Engadget</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder> Engadget</dc:rightsholder><pubDate> Tue, 13 Jun 2023 17:00:45 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1686327840</ingested><modified> 2023-06-09T16:24:03+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Lawrence Bonk]]></catego